{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were certain places you could go that were quite all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew where we shouldn't be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew which bars not to hang around in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had to hang out a little bit or they would have been suspicious.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to-- I mean, we all knew some girls, you know, naturally, and that was the best way in the world.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whenever I would have meetings with Fry, which I did quite often, we always met in cafes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, in the office, too, but finally it got so I couldn't go to the office anymore because they knew they were watching me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we'd meet in cafes, and I'd always take a girl with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, the girl couldn't under-- I always made sure she didn't understand English, and it just looked like three people sitting there, you know--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At one time, when-- when [INAUDIBLE] came to town, they locked up a lot of people, and they-- they really made a big thing when he came to town.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were very sure not to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The few times that there was a curfew, you didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only when things like when [INAUDIBLE] came to town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was questioned a couple of times, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you say 'questioned,' they didn't beat you, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, the dangerous ones when they questioned you were the nice ones, the ones who were sweet and sort of-- because they would lull you into a false sense of-- because there was one who we knew he was the worst one of all, and we warned one or two of our friends when you go there, you play right along with it.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But remember, he's worse than any of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
